# Seguros API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@authToken = {{authToken}}

## Rutas publicas

### Crear seguro (publico)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Aseguradora X",
  "nit": "800123456",
  "phone": "3001234567",
  "email": "contacto@aseguradora.com",
  "address": "Av. Principal 100",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar seguros (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/seguros/public
Accept: application/json

### Obtener seguro por id (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro/1/public
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar seguro (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro/1/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "3109876543",
  "email": "servicio@aseguradora.com",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar seguro fisicamente (publico)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro/1/public

### Baja logica de seguro (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro/1/logic/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

## Rutas protegidas (requieren token)

### Crear seguro (con auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Aseguradora Y",
  "nit": "900555444",
  "phone": "3023332211",
  "email": "contacto@aseguradoray.com",
  "address": "Carrera 15 # 45-67",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar seguros (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/seguros
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtener seguro por id (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar seguro (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "3200001122",
  "email": "soporte@aseguradoray.com",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar seguro fisicamente (con auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Baja logica de seguro (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/seguro/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}
